{"tid":1631513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"請大家唔好再推九龍塘私了post","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:23:38.000Z","uid":249608,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"93f4ab7090dd99ad721bd4375f4ac01259c91c18","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再推呢個post<br />\n我睇左段片<br />\n19:08 開始，跟本就冇影到手足打爛塊玻璃果下<br />\n淨係見到塊玻璃已經爛左，然後有前線上去同車上既人傾<br />\n聽唔到前線有兇車主，亦聽唔到有細路喊<br />\n當然樓主咪係現場? 有可能既<br />\n但亦都有可能係看圖作文/hearsay<br />\n大家自行判斷<br />\n<br />\n同埋大家真係唔好懶得去Fact check啦!! 冇證冇據可以講足咁多頁，仲引埋咁D分化撚3毛<br />\n又變左互屌post，完全浪費緊時間同資源"},{"pid":"713c2df50e76669ca865ab37ceb22c1c159b637e","tid":1631513,"uid":75959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8aa91613b0e060351e605413f2b60457c2ed3bfa","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:12.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"1c653f436f0a139f76c85e233e80f8f9db2ce64a","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96beb17e52f4bc99db9f75fd8bc9b1affa906561","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bcb46d900737da2bf39bade2107cd53707077c8","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35f869fd36b984e5a29f1258ec93d43398b11d1a","tid":1631513,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:21.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"a6579b8c4d05c86a7a0d334370e31f68ac862577","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c017219197661d25473f8948bb3cc384cf9780c","tid":1631513,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid":"df5650ac20561ae76421f95b9b9fcbc550ad91d3","tid":1631513,"uid":75543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"呢到呢幾日係勁多五毛搞分化 建議手足暫時唔好上連登住 冷靜下先講真 去twitter做文宣好過喺呢到睇post留言<br />\n<br />\n利申: 勇武和理非永不割蓆 齊上齊落"},{"pid":"7174dd2ed62db9a67881c53f64f6b0da862e3071","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fea417db6633cd930e01071fde35502f28c4a8e","tid":1631513,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:24.000Z","msg":"【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631278</a>"},{"pid":"a76fdfe02727deede073fd56ad2f124992190bf4","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7307ebedf1f1efa0dcaf3b5ce4b4a725c0c7fc0d","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3c9bd7545bfe184fede75dd0839a9e1ed699a8f","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5592991db7f5a363fbcddb93b7147c421b97dfed","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1fec28cfb31c2f48634273c6713d2eb7463a42b","tid":1631513,"uid":249608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:46:04.000Z","msg":"大家唔信